\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ---Last Seed, 17th, 4E 201---}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Couldn't wait to get out of town. The NPCs are repeating the same lines I have heard a thousand times. Kitted up with the same sort of thing that I would wear in real life: a backpack and the like. Bought a bow because, unlike Scotland, I'm not safe in the environment. It is a system that is set up not just to be observed, but to react back.}
