\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The looping, randomised animation of trout swimming up the waterfall. Such a simple little animation. The bugs flying at the water's edge. Your curiosity is rewarded; you can pluck them out of the air, a granularity of detail which still shocks.}
