\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Radiant AI is easy to interrogate into inadequacy - watching a deer on the shoreline near Riverwood, I started to see the rough edges of its animation, the planar weirdness of its stance, the repetition. I'll try approaching it.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 It does run away as you get close - very realistic, very tantalising. You cannot get close to the heart of the system, just like an individual. Things shrink away under too much enquiry, bodging, mindless grokking. Shame on me!}
