\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The character on the other bank of the lake does not wave to me. I am not inside her circle; defined geographically rather than visually. It's interesting: I don't even really want to play in third-person, as my avatar's similarity to the NPCs reinforces the stereotype.}
